"```json{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Russia carried out a major bombing campaign against Ukraine, launching a total of 151 missiles and drones overnight. The strikes targeted energy infrastructure located in and around the cities of Kharkiv, Zaporizhia and Kryvyi Rih. Ukraine\u2019s energy minister, German Galuschenko, said the attacks were intended to cause a large-scale failure in the operation of the country\u2019s energy system. On Wednesday Vladimir Putin had threatened to target the country\u2019s infrastructure in retaliation against recent Ukrainian drone attacks on refineries deep inside Russia.\",            \"english_title\": \"International Conflict\",            \"translated_version\": \"Rusia realiz\u00f3 un gran bombardeo contra Ucrania, lanzando un total de 151 misiles y drones durante la noche. Los ataques se dirigieron a la infraestructura energ\u00e9tica ubicada en y alrededor de las ciudades de Kharkiv, Zaporizhia y Kryvyi Rih. El ministro de energ\u00eda de Ucrania, German Galuschenko, dijo que los ataques ten\u00edan la intenci\u00f3n de causar un fallo a gran escala en el funcionamiento del sistema energ\u00e9tico del pa\u00eds. El mi\u00e9rcoles, Vladimir Putin amenaz\u00f3 con atacar la infraestructura del pa\u00eds en represalia por los recientes ataques con drones ucranianos a refiner\u00edas en el interior de Rusia.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Conflicto Internacional\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"China and Russia vetoed a draft resolution for an immediate ceasefire in Gaza at the UN Security Council. There were eleven votes in favour of the resolution, which was put forward by America; only Algeria, of the non-permanent members, joined China and Russia to vote against the text. The resolution tied a ceasefire deal to the release of Israeli hostages held by Hamas.\",            \"english_title\": \"Global Politics\",            \"translated_version\": \"China y Rusia vetaron una resoluci\u00f3n para un alto el fuego inmediato en Gaza en el Consejo de Seguridad de la ONU. Hubo once votos a favor de la resoluci\u00f3n, presentada por Estados Unidos; solo Argelia, de los miembros no permanentes, se uni\u00f3 a China y Rusia para votar en contra del texto. La resoluci\u00f3n vinculaba un acuerdo de alto el fuego a la liberaci\u00f3n de rehenes israel\u00edes retenidos por Hamas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Pol\u00edtica Global\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The European Commission proposed applying a tariff on grain imports from Russia and Belarus. The measure is designed to prevent the two countries from distorting European markets, as well as to counter Russia\u2019s efforts to sell grain stolen from occupied territories in Ukraine. Russia exported around \u20ac1.3bn ($1.4bn) worth of grain products to the EU last year.\",            \"english_title\": \"International Trade\",            \"translated_version\": \"La Comisi\u00f3n Europea propuso aplicar un arancel a las importaciones de granos de Rusia y Bielorrusia. La medida est\u00e1 dise\u00f1ada para evitar que los dos pa\u00edses distorsionen los mercados europeos, as\u00ed como para contrarrestar los esfuerzos de Rusia por vender granos robados de territorios ocupados en Ucrania. Rusia export\u00f3 alrededor de \u20ac1.3bn ($1.4bn) en productos de granos a la UE el a\u00f1o pasado.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Comercio Internacional\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Police in Haiti killed the head of Delmas 95, a major gang, striking a blow against Jimmy `Barbecue` Ch\u00e9rizier, who heads an alliance of criminal groups in the country\u2019s capital, Port-au-Prince. Violence has intensified in the city as Haiti\u2019s political factions attempt to form a transition council, which will fill the political vacuum left by the departure of Ariel Henry, the country\u2019s former prime minister.\",            \"english_title\": \"Security and Politics in Haiti\",            \"translated_version\": \"La polic\u00eda en Hait\u00ed mat\u00f3 al l\u00edder de Delmas 95, una banda importante, golpeando a Jimmy `Barbecue` Ch\u00e9rizier, quien lidera una alianza de grupos criminales en la capital del pa\u00eds, Puerto Pr\u00edncipe. La violencia se ha intensificado en la ciudad mientras las facciones pol\u00edticas de Hait\u00ed intentan formar un consejo de transici\u00f3n, que llenar\u00e1 el vac\u00edo pol\u00edtico dejado por la salida de Ariel Henry, el ex primer ministro del pa\u00eds.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Seguridad y Pol\u00edtica en Hait\u00ed\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"India\u2019s Aam Aadmi Party called for nationwide protests after its leader and Delhi\u2019s chief minister, Arvind Kejriwal, was arrested on corruption charges by the country\u2019s financial-crime agency. The Enforcement Directorate, which is under the control of the ruling Bharatiya Janata Party, is investigating several AAP leaders for allegedly taking kickbacks from an alcohol-licensing policy. Mr Kejriwal is challenging his arrest in a Delhi court.\",            \"english_title\": \"Political Corruption in India\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Partido Aam Aadmi de la India convoc\u00f3 a protestas en todo el pa\u00eds despu\u00e9s de que su l\u00edder y ministro principal de Delhi, Arvind Kejriwal, fuera arrestado por cargos de corrupci\u00f3n por la agencia de delitos financieros del pa\u00eds. La Direcci\u00f3n de Cumplimiento, que est\u00e1 bajo el control del gobernante Partido Bharatiya Janata, est\u00e1 investigando a varios l\u00edderes de AAP por supuestamente recibir sobornos de una pol\u00edtica de licencias de alcohol. El Sr. Kejriwal est\u00e1 impugnando su arresto en un tribunal de Delhi.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Corrupci\u00f3n Pol\u00edtica en India\"        }    ]}```"